{"tid":645114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(懷舊一下)肉蒲團—色以外的情","createTime":"2018-04-27T20:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T04:58:04.000Z","uid":47614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c12844b45e04980260e3a1d798457911a1c866d","tid":645114,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T20:58:08.000Z","msg":"唔講咩露lin 愛情動作片 亦都唔使po潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實啱啱翻睇完肉蒲團，俾我嘅係講緊一種真情高於物慾嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成套戲係好做到呢個對比 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">所以我都唔知開唔開喺影視台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n佢最後 「你若無情我便休 往事如昨易白頭」 真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未央生風流快活，鐵玉香就錯識人 <br />\n幾經波折之後先發覺原來一生極樂並唔係嗰短暫嘅刺激，而係嗰份一直都喺度嘅真情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相信喺而家呢個社會，好多人都做唔到，就算明 都已經後悔莫及<br />\n<br />\n首片尾歌都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zQiwVtDMq1A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzQiwVtDMq1A&d=3Zcl6KWI0%2FyePqdkTz%2Bzb%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d1737eb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zQiwVtDMq1A</a>"},{"pid":"723da3ff5a5d1fb197b50baf303400ca4c2c3dcd","tid":645114,"uid":75827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T21:15:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬係講3d肉蒲團個齣？ 搵日睇返先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916cf2349caca2ef66bd495d048251675697d37c","tid":645114,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"723da3ff5a5d1fb197b50baf303400ca4c2c3dcd","tid":645114,"uid":75827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T21:15:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬係講3d肉蒲團個齣？ 搵日睇返先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"